Irin wannan yanayin na karuwar yawan masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU / EEA da Burtaniya ya tabbatar da cewa, duk da cewa matakai sun bambanta tsakanin ƙasashe, yaduwar COVID-19 tana ci gaba da haɓaka cikin sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Bisa ga kwarewar Italiya, ƙasashe, asibitoci da raka'a na kulawa mai tsanani dole ne su haɓaka shirye-shiryen su don magance ƙaruwar masu kamuwa da COVID-19 waɗanda ke buƙatar kulawa ta musamman da kulawa mai tsanani.
A ranar 31 ga watan Disamba na 2019, an samu wasu mutane da suka kamu da cutar sankarar bargo da ba a san dalilin da ya sa ba a birnin Wuhan na lardin Hubei na kasar Sin.
A ranar 9 ga watan Janairun 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka ta kasar Sin ta bayyana dalilin cutar a matsayin sabon coronavirus wanda yanzu ake kira coronavirus 2 na cutar sankarar bargo 2-SARS-CoV.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, cutar da ke haifar da 2-SARS-CoV an san ta da cutar coronavirus COVID-19.
Shaida har zuwa yau ta nuna cewa kashi 80% na mutanen da ke fama da COVID-19 suna fama da rashin lafiya mai sauƙi, wato cututtukan numfashi ba tare da cutar huhu ba ko tare da cutar huhu kuma yawancin suna murmurewa.
Kashi 14% na masu kamuwa da COVID-19 suna buƙatar asibiti, kuma sauran kashi 6% na marasa lafiya suna buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani.
Yawan mutuwar mutane da ke fama da cutar COVID-19 a cikin marasa lafiya ya kai kusan 4%.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun kimanta yanayin yanayin COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa ta EU/EEA da Burtaniya kuma mun kwatanta shi da yanayin lardin Hubei na China.
Mun kuma kwatanta yawan adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19 a cikin EU / EU Economic Area da UK tare da adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a Italiya a cikin lokacin Janairu 31-15 Maris 2020.
Cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU/AER da UK
Bayan China, COVID-19 ya haifar da ƙarin ci gaban ƙasa kuma yawan yaduwar cutar coronavirus a sauran ƙasashe na duniya yana kama da na ƙasar Sin.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Darakta Janar na Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana cutar ta COVID-19 a matsayin annoba ta duniya.
A ranar 5 ga Maris, a cewar Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri da abokan aikinsa sun ba da rahoton farkon cutar COVID-19 da aka tabbatar a Turai kamar yadda WHO ta bayyana.
A cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA, an tabbatar da shari'o'in farko guda uku a ranar 24 ga Janairu 2020 a cikin mutanen da suka dawo daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei na China.
A ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an samu kararraki na COVID-19 a duk ƙasashe 30 na Tarayyar Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Burtaniya, wanda ya haifar da kararraki 39,768 da mutuwar 1,727 a cikin wannan lokacin tsakanin 31 ga Disamba, 2019, daga cikin 17,750 da mutuwar 1,441 a Italiya kadai.
Samun adadin masu kamuwa da cutar da kuma yawan adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19.
Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC), ta ba da rahoton adadin masu cutar COVID-19 a duk ƙasashen duniya, ana samun su ne kawai daga kafofin hukuma kamar ma'aikatun kiwon lafiya na ƙasashe, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na yanki da WHO kuma ana sabunta su kowace rana da ƙarfe 8:00 na safe.
An yi amfani da wannan bayanan don kimanta yanayin COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU da Burtaniya da kuma kwatanta su da Italiya.
A matsayin mai lura da ci gaban shari'o'in COVID-19 masu aiki, mun bincika ƙimar raguwar kwanaki 14 na COVID-19 don haka muna ɗaukar yanayin yanayin COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa ta EU da Burtaniya daga Janairu 1 zuwa Maris 15, 2020.
Mun kuma ba da adadin adadin masu cutar da aka ruwaito a kowace ƙasa a karfe 8:00 na safe ranar 15 ga Maris idan aka kwatanta da adadin a Italiya a tsakanin Janairu 31 zuwa Maris 15.
Yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU da UK
Matsayin da aka samu na kwanaki 14 na cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU da UK gabaɗaya yayi daidai da na lardin Hubei na China (Figure 1.1).
A cikin ƙasashen EU da Burtaniya gabaɗaya, yawan kamuwa da COVID-19 ya fara ƙaruwa a ranar 21 ga Fabrairu kuma ya sami ƙaruwa sosai a ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020 (bayanan hoto).
Wannan ya fi yawaita saboda saurin karuwar adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a Italiya, amma duk sauran ƙasashen EU da Burtaniya sun nuna irin wannan ci gaban a cikin yawan mutuwar COVID-19 a cikin nasu.
Figure 2 ya nuna adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU da UK da Italiya a cikin lokacin daga 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Wannan ya nuna cewa a karfe 8:00 na safiyar ranar 15 ga Maris, yawan adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a sauran ƙasashen Tarayyar Turai 15 da Burtaniya sun kai adadin adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a Italiya a makonni 3 ko ƙasa da haka.
Sakamakon bincikenmu ya nuna cewa adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU da UK suna ƙaruwa cikin sauri.
Hanyoyin da ake gani na yawan kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 sun nuna cewa wannan yaduwar tana ci gaba a irin wannan saurin a duk ƙasashe.
Wannan duk da cewa ƙasashe suna cikin matakai daban-daban na rayuwa da kuma ba su da daidaito a cikin amsar lafiyar jama'a ta ƙasa, da kuma bambance-bambance a cikin ma'anar yanayin da kuma ladabi na gano marasa lafiya don gwaji don tabbatar da kamuwa da COVID-19.
A farkon watan Maris na 2020, likitocin yankunan da ke cikin Italiya sun bayyana halin da ake ciki cewa kusan kashi 10% na masu cutar COVID-19 suna buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani, kuma kafofin watsa labarai sun bayyana cewa asibitoci da raka'a na kulawa mai tsanani a waɗannan yankuna sun kai iyakar ƙarfin su.
Bayanan kwantar da marasa lafiya na COVID-19 a asibiti da kuma a cikin cibiyoyin kulawa mai tsanani a cikin EU / EEA a halin yanzu suna da kashi 6% da 1% na lokuta, bi da bi (ba a nuna bayanai ba).
