Wani bincike da aka gudanar a watan Nuwamba na 2010 ya nuna bambancin da ke tsakanin yawan gadajen kula da marasa lafiya a Turai, inda a Jamus akwai gadaje 29.2 da kuma a Portugal akwai gadaje 4.2 ga kowane mutum 100,000.
