An gano haɗuwa da beta-CoVs a cikin dabbobi masu kama da SARS-CoV-2, wanda ke nuna cewa dabbobi masu kama da su na iya aiki a matsayin matsakaiciyar mai karɓar bakuncin, ko kuma beta-CoVs na pangolin na iya fitar da kwayar halitta don sabon nau'in SARS-CoV-2.
Ko da yake tambayoyi sun kasance, babu wata hujja da ta nuna cewa SARS-CoV-2 ya haifar da mutum, da gangan ko kuma ba da gangan ba.
Cutar coronavirus ta samo asali ne daga ɓarkewar cutar SARS-CoV-2.
Binciken kwayar cutar coronavirus a cikin barbashi da sauran dabbobi ya canza ra'ayoyinmu game da mahimmancin asalin dabbobi da kuma yadda dabbobi ke ɗaukar kwayar cutar coronavirus don watsawa ga mutane.
Shaidar da aka samu ta nuna cewa SARS-CoV, SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV-2 sun ƙunshi asalin ƙuda kuma an watsa su ta hanyar kwayoyin halitta zuwa mutane.
Tun da yake kamuwa da SARS-CoV ya samo asali ne daga hulɗar mutum da dabbobi a cikin kasuwa, rufe kasuwanni da kashe dabbobi zai iya kawo ƙarshen cutar SARS.
Don wannan dalili, dabbobi masu kama da dabbobi suna buƙatar dakatar da su daga kasuwa don hana yaduwar dabbobi, saboda gano asalin beta-coronavirus da ke da alaƙa da SARS-CoV-2.
Koyaya, ko kuma yadda SARS-CoV-2 ke yaduwa ga mutane ta hanyar pangolins da sauran dabbobi masu shayarwa ya kasance don tantancewa a cikin gwaji na gaba.
A gefe guda, MERS-CoV ya daɗe yana ɓoye.
Waɗannan raƙuman suna da mahimmancin hanyar sufuri, saboda sune tushen kayan abinci na nama, madara, fata da abinci ga mazauna yankin.
An fi yaduwa a Gabas ta Tsakiya da Afirka.
Saboda haka, ba za a iya kashe dukan rakuma ba don magance cutar MERS, kamar yadda aka yi a kasuwar dabbobi a China, don hana yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 da SARS-CoV-2.
Don dakatar da wannan yaduwar MERS, dole ne a yi ƙoƙari sosai don haɓaka maganin rigakafi mai tasiri ga MERS-CoV don raƙuma, tare da matakan kula da kamuwa da cuta.
Duk da yake ba za mu iya kawar da wannan kwayar cutar ba, sabon nau'in kwayar halitta na iya haifar da yaduwar ta.
Yawancin nau'ikan coronavirus na dabbobi suna yaduwa a cikin yankunan tsaunuka.
Musamman, ƙwayoyin cuta na coronavirus waɗanda ke da asali na dabba sun bambanta.
Akwai yiwuwar cewa kwayar cutar coronavirus ta dabbobi za ta iya haɓaka da daidaitawa, wanda zai haifar da haɗuwa da sabbin kwayar cutar coronavirus waɗanda za su iya zama masu saurin yaduwa da / ko kisa ga mutane a nan gaba.
A wasu sassa na kasar Sin, ya kamata a dakatar da cin abincin namun daji don rage hulɗar da ba ta dace ba tsakanin mutane da dabbobi.
Tare da cututtukan SARS, MERS da coronavirus, ya kamata a sami shiri mafi kyau da shirye-shiryen amsawa da amsawa.
A gaskiya ma, yawancin ƙwayoyin cuta sun kasance a wannan duniyar a cikin dogon lokaci.
Sun kasance a cikin yanayin da suka dace, har sai akwai damar da za su yada.
Kodayake jemage suna da halaye da yawa waɗanda ke taimakawa wajen yada kwayar cutar, haɗarin haɗuwa da ɗan adam tare da jemage da sauran dabbobin daji za a iya rage su idan an koya wa mutane su guji su.
Ana buƙatar ci gaba da lura da dabbobi masu shayarwa don fahimtar yanayin CoVs da kuma yanayin halitta, wanda ke nuna fa'idodi na hana yaduwar dabbobi zuwa mutane da kuma ci gaban yaduwar su.
A ƙarshe, hanya mafi inganci don hana dabbobi daga ɗaukar cutar ita ce nisantar mutane daga yanayin da dabbobi ke ɗaukar kwayar cutar.
Har yanzu ba a gano wasu abubuwa game da asalin SARS-CoV-2 a cikin dabbobi ba.
Da farko, idan kwari ya kawo SARS-CoV-2 zuwa pangolin, zai zama da kyau a ga yadda kwari da pangolin ke da irin yanayin da suke da shi.
Na biyu, idan kwari suna da babban rawa wajen watsawa kai tsaye ga mutane, za a buƙaci a ƙayyade yadda mutane ke hulɗa da kwari.
Na uku, idan dabba mai mahimmanci ta uku ta kasance kamar mai kula da kwayoyin halitta, yadda ta yi hulɗa da mutane daban-daban, da bats da penguins, dole ne a bayyana.
A ƙarshe, saboda yawancin dabbobi masu shayarwa suna kamuwa da dabbobi na gida, waɗanda zasu iya zama masu saurin kamuwa da SARS-CoV-2, dole ne a gudanar da bincike da gwaji don kamuwa da cuta.
Ko dai ɗan kunama ne, pangolin ko kuma wani dabba mai shayarwa, ana tsammanin SARS-CoV-2 ko kuma wasu ƙwayoyin cuta masu kama da su, za a iya gano su a cikin yanayin ƙwayoyin a nan gaba.
Ci gaba da bincike ya nuna yadda SARS-CoV-2 ke ci gaba a cikin dabbobi, tare da ƙoƙarin kawar da cutar a cikin mutane.
Ana buƙatar sabunta ma'aunin gano COVID-19 "Lallai ne" da "Lallai ne".
A ranar 6 ga Fabrairun 2020, ƙungiyarmu ta buga jagorar shawarwari na gaggawa don ganowa da magance cutar 2019 (2019-nCoV) ta sabuwar coronavirus, wannan jagorar ta ba da kwarewarmu kuma ta nuna ƙalubalen da ke tattare da cutar a duniya.
Koyaya, cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19) sabuwar cuta ce, kuma muna ci gaba da haɓaka faɗakarwarmu da iliminmu bisa ga binciken da ake ci gaba da samu da kuma ƙwarewar aikin asibiti; sabili da haka, ana ci gaba da sabunta dabarun bincike da magani.
A cikin wannan rubutun, mun amsa ga wata sharhi game da jagorarmu kuma mun ba da sabon ma'aunin ganewa don "Laifin da ake zargi" da "Laifin da aka tabbatar" bisa ga sabon Jagorar Ganowa da Kula da COVID-19 (Shirya ta 7) da Hukumar Kiwon Lafiyar Jama'ar Jamhuriyar Sin ta fitar.
A watan Disamba na 2019, sabon coronavirus na 2019 (2019-nCoV) ya fara bayyana, wanda yanzu aka fi sani da cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-2019) kuma an sake sanya wa kwayar cutar SARS-CoV-2 (SARS-CoV-2).
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba ta duniya.
Don yaƙi da cutar SARS-CoV-2, ƙungiyarmu ta samar da jagorar shawarwari na gaggawa wanda aka buga akan layi a cikin Military Medical Research a ranar 6 ga Fabrairu, 2020.
Tun lokacin da aka buga shi, ya sami kulawa sosai.
Lura: Kodayake COVID-19 sabuwar cuta ce, faɗakarwarmu da iliminmu suna ƙaruwa a hankali bisa ga binciken da ake ci gaba da samu da kuma ƙwarewar aikin asibiti; sabili da haka, ana ci gaba da sabunta dabarun bincike da magani.
Misali, Hukumar Kula da Lafiya ta Jamhuriyar Jama'ar Sin ta fitar da Jagororin Gano da Kula da COVID-19 (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/), tsakanin 16 ga Janairu, 2020 zuwa 3 ga Maris, 2020, sun fitar da jimlar lambobi bakwai tare da wasu abubuwan da aka canza sosai.
Yanzu jagororinmu sun kasance maganganun Zhou et al. Hut, wanda ya ba da shawara mai sauƙi don yin la'akari da kwarewarsu ta asibiti.
Ayyukan su sun ba da sabon tabbaci ga jagororinmu kuma sun nuna godiya ga wannan annoba ta duniya.
Muna goyon bayan wannan aiki mai muhimmanci kuma muna godiya da su.
Koyaya, aikin su yana buƙatar sabuntawa bisa ga sabbin jagororin ganowa da maganin COVID-19 (matakin gwaji na bakwai) da sabbin bincike.
A cikin sashi na bakwai (Maris 3, 2020), don tabbatar da cewa yanayin da ake zargi ya kamata ya haɗa kowane ɗayan abubuwan da ke tattare da tarihin cutar tare da abubuwa biyu na alamun asibiti don yin cikakken bincike, ko kuma ya kamata ya ƙunshi abubuwa uku na alamun asibiti idan tarihin cutar ba shi da kyau:
Tarihin cutar: (1) Tarihin tafiya ko zama a Wuhan da kewayenta, ko wasu al'ummomin da aka ba da rahoton cutar COVID-19 a cikin kwanaki 14 da suka gabata kafin fara bayyanar cututtuka; (2) Tarihin haɗuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 (tare da gwajin nucleic acid mai kyau); (3) Tarihin haɗuwa da marasa lafiya tare da ko tare da cututtukan numfashi a Wuhan da kewayenta, ko wasu al'ummomin da aka ba da rahoton COVID-19 a cikin kwanaki 14 da suka gabata kafin bayyanar cututtuka; (4) Tarihin haɗuwa da wasu tabbatattun shari'o'i (>= 2 lokuta da / ko tare da cututtukan na respiratory polypes waɗanda suka faru a cikin makonni 2 a cikin ƙananan wurare, kamar gidaje, ofisoshi, makarantu, da sauransu).
Alamar asibiti: (1) har zuwa da / ko alamun cututtukan numfashi; (2) tare da halaye na cutar COVID-19; (3) ƙarancin adadin ƙwayoyin farin jini wanda ke nuna ƙimar al'ada, raguwa, ko ƙarancin ƙididdigar ƙwayoyin cuta a farkon farawa.
Dole ne a tabbatar da ganewar asali na tabbataccen yanayin bisa ga yanayin da ake zargi cewa kowane alamun cutar ko hujja ta ƙwayar cuta yana da kyau kamar haka: (1) gwajin lokaci na PCR mai kyau na SARS-CoV-2; (2) cikakken jerin kwayoyin halittar kwayar cutar wanda ke nuna asalin kwayar cutar coronavirus; (3) tabbatacce ga ƙwayoyin IgM na musamman da IgG na SARS-CoV-2 a cikin gwajin ƙwayar cuta; ko canji a cikin ƙwayoyin IgG na SARS-CoV-2 daga mara kyau zuwa tabbatacce, ko kuma ƙimar => 4 sau a lokacin farfadowa sama da lokacin kamuwa da cutar.
Za mu iya ganin cewa an ƙara gwajin PCR na ainihi don nucleic acid a cikin hanyar numfashi ko samfurin jini zuwa shafi na biyu (Janairu 18, 2020) da shafi na uku (Janairu 22, 2020).
An ƙara gano cutar a cikin samfurin jini a shafi na huɗu (Janairu 27, 2020) da shafi na biyar (Fabrairu 8, 2020); sannan an ƙara shaidar ƙwayar cuta a shafi na bakwai.
Waɗannan gyare-gyare sun dogara ne akan ci gaba da aikin masu bincike don neman kayan aikin gano kwayar nucleic acid don saurin ganewa, tare da samfurori na numfashi waɗanda suka haɗa da samfurin jini, wanda ya haɓaka wadatar bambancin samfurin, kuma ya taimaka wajen samar da sakamako mai kyau na antibody na musamman a cikin sigogi masu tabbaci.
Bugu da ƙari, akwai ƙarin shaidu da ke nuna cewa muna bukatar mu kula da cututtukan da ba su da alamun cutar.
