Wani binciken kimiyya na Danish na 2012 ya gano cewa wanke hannu da yawa na iya haifar da ƙwanƙwasawa da yanayin fata da aka sani da ƙwanƙwasa hannu, wanda ya zama ruwan dare a cikin ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya.
Ana ganin yawan wanke hannu a matsayin daya daga cikin alamun bayyanar cututtuka na OCD.
Akwai lokuta biyar a rana da wanke hannu da sabulu ke da mahimmanci don rage haɗarin kamuwa da cuta ta hanyar stool; bayan wanka (shan fitsari da fitsari), bayan wanke tufafin yara (canza tufafi), kafin cin abinci da kafin da bayan shirya abinci ko shirya nama, kifi da kaji.
