Lokacin da akwai ƙananan ƙoƙari don rage keɓewar zamantakewa, ana iya aiwatar da matakan nisantar zamantakewa kamar ƙin tafiya da tarurruka da sauran manyan tarurruka kamar ilimin likita ko tarurrukan addini ko cin abinci tare a cikin kantin, ƙara tsawon lokaci tsakanin tebur da shirya tafiye-tafiye da hutun ɗalibai da iyakance balaguron da ba dole ba da kuma amfani da wurin ofishin likita don yara masu alamun mura.
Lokacin da akwai yaduwar cutar a cikin al'umma, duk da kasancewar hanyoyin nisantar zamantakewa, ana iya yin la'akari da tsawaita hutun makaranta. Don aiwatar da dokar hukumar don aiwatar da ayyukan yau da kullun, CDC ta ɗauki haɗarin lafiya na kai tsaye da ƙarancin.
